<subSubSection id="C3796513FFEAFFF6FC8BF983FB0016FE" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BDC3698FFEAFFF6FC8BF983FB0016FE" blockId="2.[869,1494,1562,1683]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FC8BF983FC33165E" bold="true" box="[869,993,1562,1587]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Type data:</emphasis>
This species was apparently described based on a single male collected by János Anisits in 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FA86F9A3FA01163E" box="[1384,1491,1594,1619]" country="Paraguay" name="Asuncion" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Asunción</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3747608FFEAFFF6FC89F9C3FC1D161E" box="[871,975,1626,1651]" name="Paraguay" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
. The current condition and depository of the 
<typeStatus id="54D8883AFFEAFFF6FC8BF9E3FC1816FE" box="[869,970,1658,1683]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">holotype</typeStatus>
are currently unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3796513FFEAFFF6FC8BF923FB4F17DE" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BDC3698FFEAFFF6FC8BF923FB4F17DE" blockId="2.[869,1494,1722,1971]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FC8BF923FC3E16BE" bold="true" box="[869,1004,1722,1747]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Comments:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FC10F923FB4D16BE" author="Moure, J. S." box="[1022,1183,1722,1747]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="385 - 394" refId="ref4435" refString="Moure, J. S. 1950. Alguns agrupamentos novos de abelhas neotropicais (Hymenoptera, Apoidea). Dusenia, 1 (6): 385 - 394." type="journal article" year="1950">Moure (1950)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned the variability in the coloration of the pubescence of 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FABEF943FBCC177E" authority="Burmeister, 1876" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1876" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Hemisia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectoralis">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FABEF943FA07169E" box="[1360,1493,1754,1779]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C. pectoralis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FC8BF963FBCC177E" author="Burmeister, H." box="[869,1054,1786,1811]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="151 - 183" refId="ref3949" refString="Burmeister, H. 1876. Hymenopterologische Mittheilungen. Stettinger Entomologische Zeitung, 37 (1 / 3): 151 - 183." type="journal article" year="1876">Burmeister,1876</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FBD0F963FB60177E" box="[1086,1202,1786,1811]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obsoleta">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FBD0F963FB60177E" box="[1086,1202,1786,1811]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C.obsoleta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) indicating that the varieties described of that species must be suppressed, which would include 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FBE5F8A3FACE173E" authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1908" box="[1035,1308,1850,1875]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Hemisia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="pectoralis" variety="clypeata">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FBE5F8A3FB5F173E" box="[1035,1165,1850,1875]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C. pectoralis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FB2FF8A3FACE173E" box="[1217,1308,1850,1875]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">clypeata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FABAF8A3FC1A171E" authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1908" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Hemisia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="pectoralis" variety="flava">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FABAF8A3FA04173E" box="[1364,1494,1850,1875]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C. pectoralis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FC7DF8C3FC1A171E" box="[915,968,1882,1907]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">flava</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see below). However, the synonymy between this latter 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FC36F8E3FB8717FE" box="[984,1109,1914,1939]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" rank="variety" variety="and">variety and</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFEAFFF6FBB5F8E3FB0017FE" box="[1115,1234,1914,1939]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obsoleta">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FBB5F8E3FB0017FE" box="[1115,1234,1914,1939]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C. obsoleta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was only formally indicated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FC24F803FB4B17DE" author="Moure, J. S. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F." box="[970,1177,1946,1971]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref4557" refString="Moure, J. S.; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F. 2007. Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure, J. S.; Urban, D. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. (Orgs.). Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region, Curitiba, Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia. p. 83 - 142." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Moure 
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FBF6F803FB9917DE" box="[1048,1099,1946,1971]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">et al.</emphasis>
(2007)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
